## Instance Scheduler

Eventbridge is used to schedule and trigger Lambda functions that automatically start and stop instances on member accounts from Monday to Friday at scheduled times.

For detailed guidance and setup, please refer to the Instance Scheduler repository (https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-instance-scheduler).

For monitoring and alerts - cloudwatch alarm set up and configued to notify SNS topic and integrated with PagerDuty.
https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-terraform-pagerduty-integration - This module can be used for integrating SNS topics with PagerDuty & more guidance can be found at : https://user-guide.modernisation-platform.service.justice.gov.uk/user-guide/integrating-alarms-with-pagerduty-with-slack.html#integrating-cloudwatch-alarms-with-pagerduty-and-slack


##  Microsoft Active Directory Controllers 

Deploying EC2 instances to host Microsoft Domain Controller service in live and non_live VPCs. Azure.noms.root and azure.hmpp.root AD DS infrastructure migrated from Azure FixNGo and managed by DSO team.

## VPC  
Create two VPCs:
- non_live_data VPC
- live_data VPC
Configure appropriate subnets, route tables, and security groups for each VPC and connect Transit Gateway for communication





